summary: for those who didn’t get on what I like in Detective Pikachu’s “realism” is more to the idea of the world building and details...
body:
for those who didn’t get on what I like in Detective Pikachu’s “realism” is more to the idea of the world building and details than the CGI itself- the CGI is amazing indeed but I imagined something else close to real-life animals for the “realistic” Pokemon in my head.

The touch of realism in the world building and detail, however… I am in love with and I long for it owo
